Package de.yamass.redg.runtime

Interface RedGEntity

public interface RedGEntity
This is the interface for every entity that can be inserted into a database by RedG. Every generated entity class implements this interface

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    List<RedGEntity>
    getDependencies()
    Returns a list of all other RedGEntitys this entity depends on (has foreign keys to).
    String
    getPreparedStatementString()
    Returns a valid SQL statement using '?'
    Object[]
    getPreparedStatementValues()
    Returns an array of objects that contains the values for the placeholders specified in getPreparedStatementString().
    AttributeMetaInfo[]
    getPreparedStatementValuesMetaInfos()
    Returns an array of the sql types for the objects from getPreparedStatementValues().
    String
    getSQLString()
    Returns a valid SQL insert statement that can be used to persist this entity in the database.
